definitions.definition: ( provincial , Northern England ) To earn , earn by labor; earn money or one's living.
( provincial , Northern England ) To thrive or grow; to ripen.

main_definition: ( provincial , Northern England ) To earn , earn by labor; earn money or one's living.
secondary_definitions: ( provincial , Northern England ) To thrive or grow; to ripen.

definitions.definition: To make addle; to grow addle; to muddle .
To cause fertilised eggs to lose viability , by killing the developing embryo within through shaking , piercing , freezing or oiling , without breaking the shell.
